  "texts": [
    "The methane combustion system was initialized with 100 CH 4 molecules and 200 O 2 molecules.",
    "All molecules were inserted using Packmol and ensuring that all molecules were separated by at least 2.0 Å.",
    "The cubic simulation box length was 37.60 Å, resulting in a density of 0.25 g cc -1.",
    "The temperature was initialized to 3,000 K by Maxwell-Boltzmann distribution.",
    "Langevin dynamics were run for 1 ns with a time step of 0.1 fs and with a friction constant of 0.01."
  ],
